sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Pytest as Pytest runner
    participant ProcFactory as rabbitmq_proc fixture (session)
    participant RabbitProcess as RabbitMQ process
    participant ClientFactory as rabbitmq fixture (function)
    participant RabbitMQ as RabbitMQ broker

    Pytest->>ProcFactory: request rabbitmq_proc
    ProcFactory->>RabbitProcess: start process
    loop per test
        Pytest->>ClientFactory: request rabbitmq connection
        ClientFactory->>RabbitProcess: open AMQP connection
        Pytest->>RabbitMQ: run test using queues/exchanges
        Pytest->>RabbitMQ: teardown: delete non-amq.* queues/exchanges
        Pytest->>ClientFactory: close client
    end
    ProcFactory->>RabbitProcess: stop process (end of session)
